{"tid":1308893,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"乘勝追擊，不然共匪會報仇。","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T06:26:08.000Z","uid":74527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd625ac7447bc33648c7bf92b4044ff3882264dd","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>乘勝追擊，不然共匪會報仇。</strong></span><br />\n香港政府由７月１日開始至今既行為，反映出完全冇曬政治力。<br />\n香港人已經過左第一關，然後香港人要救港就要透過外國勢力，即係美國。<br />\n由６月９號至今，侵侵出過稿、RUBIO係獨立日出文、安全部直接警告中國，係美國回應香港人係G20既請願。依家又到返香港人配合美國，令美國同中國碰撞，比壓力中國，令中國意識到香港死左，佢條命都唔長，又係提醒美國有西貢淪陷一事，比佢地知香港係重要之地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TW266gm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTW266gm.jpg&h=312c43cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就係重點，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二波！白宮聯署！</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持美國推出並通過&lt;香港人權和民主法案&gt;</span></span><br />\n點解？睇圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfGDcWC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfGDcWC.png&h=badfdba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地就算輸，都要搵Ｄ官同我地一齊死！<br />\n然而，香港依家有一大機會利用美國去奪回普選，然後香港人拎返主導權，保衛憲法，保護香港實然主權，自我解救。<br />\n各位要貼就貼TRUMP2020同美國國旗，一黎回應美國，二黎促成通過&lt;香港人權和民主法案&gt;，三黎增加藍絲同共匪訊息量，使其腦癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n最後，利用連儂牆，貼到周圍係，貼到Ｄ仆街日日訓醒都要CHECK下自己美國國藉同戶口係唔係度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dU9jCH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dU9jCH.png&h=52bb7c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">PRESIDENT TRUMP PLEASE LIBERATE HK!<br />\n<br />\nONLY PRESIDENT TRUMP CAN SAVE US!<br />\n<br />\nTRUMP2020 MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN!<br />\n<br />\n美軍未來我邀請!<br />\n美軍來了我帶路!</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0K0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=7c610601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>不可一，不可再，機會得一次，不然你我會係大灣區見。</strong>"},{"pid":"69b500450fc1af0885b07395d003f0604b7d6e1b","tid":1308893,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"bd5b6c13b85b5cb1bd6c8b6ca199262bdc090c35","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fdbbc98997c50effc92789cc8477e6fc3bb059","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3bf5da5925344bb7a14a4ede0048defb3b68b3","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9231e246a35591f1587751a4bcf3d11476fde87","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018bc1f02383fc05e71023e24bd34ac035a22682","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbWWKcD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbWWKcD.jpg&h=356f918f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人係G20請 種下既種子發芽。<br />\n記住，仙豆得一粒。 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"3a5f3d90fee07475dc45ee1aa4b5904072e0aed3","tid":1308893,"uid":74527,"